com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.Match

  • public final class Match
extends java.lang.Object
    Match represents an element found in the code that is interesting for the target. It's defined by the generating target, the element found and a context element. The context element is the containing TLElement corresponding to the TargetSearchLevel (e.g. for TargetSearchLevel.METHOD, it's the TLMethod containing the found element).
